::Zeus/Mosquitor/Shredder::

Zeus arrives at base, putting Set in a CR chamber and entering one himself.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Mosquitor flies into the predacon base, going to a CR chamber.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Shredder stumbles into the predacon base, mildly surprised that the autoguns 
hadn't killed him. He speaks into his comm-link.

"Megatron? Quickstrike?"
